statements.sql: select * from `presensi` inner join `karyawan` on `karyawan`.`id_karyawan` = `presensi`.`id_karyawan` where `presensi`.`id_karyawan` = '12' and month(`presensi`.`masuk`) = '10' and year(`presensi`.`masuk`) = '2022' and time(`presensi`.`masuk`) <= '9:00:00' and (`presensi`.`status` = 1 or `presensi`.`status` = 3)
select count(*) as aggregate from `presensi` where `id_karyawan` = '12' and month(`masuk`) = '10' and year(`masuk`) = '2022' and (`status` = 1 or `status` = 3) and time(`masuk`) <= '9:00:00'
select * from `presensi` where `id_karyawan` = '12' and `status` = 3 and month(`masuk`) = '10' and year(`masuk`) = '2022' and time(`masuk`) > '17:00:00'
